room_title: Escape room "The Cabin 2 - The Sequel" by Downtown Escape Rooms in Sherman
room_description: The Cabin 2 is a sequel to the Cabin Room.  Just when you thought you had called 911 to save you and your sister Lisa, the men who kidnapped you intercept the phone call and give new twist on the demands to save both you and your sister.  Can you meet the demands before time runs out to save the both of you.................​​
